ote><br />\n有試過同樣情況，都係少/冇菜，有血<br />\n你飲多啲水，每日兩 以上L ,幾日就會好番</blockquote><br />\n即刻落街買左d 生果食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能住hell 既關係 成日廢事煮去買m記食<br />\n一星期都唔會食到菜乜濟<br />\n琴日淆底先開始食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無機會食菜就多啲食火龍果，好通便"},{"pid":"5d946f51e2298c78d6f4b11eea4fe73f5982541a","tid":292992,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"通常你自己嚇自己 嚇得耐就有<br />\n<br />\n但你唔理就會無事<br />\n<br />\nbtw 排期照下腸鏡<br />\n<br />\n發炎，生瘡，生息肉，啲屎太硬刮傷左都有機會"},{"pid":"40585398a5cb9e056948981f30f860d7b84b3996","tid":292992,"uid":46011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7b5fb1bc36c43494723199eaf00838df7268240","tid":292992,"uid":123195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"太大力？"},{"pid":"4ed6a8679822a6b324ca5d65f5ce849ea6d49e43","tid":292992,"uid":19499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁 睇左醫生最後係痔瘡黎 食左一兩個月藥同埋日日瘋狂飲水就無事"},{"pid":"e4e3e63483f4e95924c98b6c80ec797585f1c316","tid":292992,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"白癡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b0feeee5bd31186cd8646faf93ddf2cf6e26cc","tid":292992,"uid":74326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1de8f5740aea4a19bf5fde38f6b6bbf78347bd6","tid":292992,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"鮮血多數都係痔瘡/柯損左<br />\n黑屎先大獲<br />\n利伸：老母教"},{"pid":"260d3bc2bc30921bb50391c3a698c049f3ea2e0d","tid":292992,"uid":116976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:12:49.000Z","msg":"瘡，係咁多"},{"pid":"6439605705f4383f3c08e2117f9c862cfc566ed5","tid":292992,"uid":76984,